Content: Headlight went out while riding last night. No start this morning. Battery full. Rear light and front and rear turning signals work and horn, headLight and ignition don't. Bike bump starts. Starter solenoid fuse intact. Holding ignition button while using a screwdriver to bridge the leads on the solenoid engages the starter, but didn't start it. 2023 honda xr150l 300 miles.
